---
description: Agent Planning file-based workflow rules
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: false
---

Use Agent Planning for multi-step work.

- Keep task plan, findings, and progress separate.
- Do not mark work done without evidence.
- Keep temporary plan state under `.opendock/plans/`.
- Run `node .opendock/harness/opendock__agent-planning/check.mjs` before handoff when possible.
